    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "DIRECTOR, FBI",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "SAC, SEATTLE",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "REPORTS ON ALLEGED SIGHTING OF SUBMARINES,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "PARACHUTE LANDINGS, FLASHING LIGHTS, ETC.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "ESPIONAGE",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "6/18/54",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "It has been the experience of this office that during this season,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "from now until winter, there is received a considerable number of alleged",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "reports on sighting of submarines, flashing lights, parachute landings,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "flying saucers, etc. In every instance when such reports are received,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "the information is immediately disseminated to DIO, 13 ND, U. S. Navy;",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "OSI, USAF; and G-3, U. S. Army.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Inasmuch as Seattle is the District Headquarters for the Intelligence",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "Agencies in the Pacific Northwest, reports received, usually from the USCG,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "concerning incidents in the state of Oregon are immediately reported to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "that office as well as the Intelligence Agencies.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "Many of the reports are of a nebulous type, impossible of corroborating,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "and of doubtful authenticity. Some, by preliminary inquiry and evaluation,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "prove to be without foundation. However, as stated above, reports of this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "type are immediately disseminated to the Intelligence Agencies without",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "evaluation, followed by additional information as obtained.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "This office has no control of the dissemination of these reports",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "on a \"spot\" basis by the local intelligence offices to their Headquarters",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "in Washington, D. C. The Bureau will recall the widespread dissemination",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "given by the military agencies of \"Radio Message March 13, 1953, Interpreted",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "as Calling for Mobilization of Communist Party\" (SAC Letter #23, dated",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "3/31/53).",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "The purpose of this letter is to advise the Bureau that in all",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "instances immediate dissemination is made of all unusual incidents that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "appear to have any military significance. This office also acts as a co-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "ordinator on all reports to be certain that all interested agencies are",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "cognizant.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "The Bureau may be assured that it will be kept advised of all",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "significant incidents as they arise but will not be bothered with every",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "trivial incident that occurs unless instructed.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
